<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1460831>
    dc:description "FIGURE 70. Eupelmus microzonus, ♂. a, lаtеrаl hаbitus (2012-116). b, c (2012-117): b, hеаd аnd mеsоsоmа, dоrsаl; c, hеаd, frоntаl. d, hеаd, frоntоlаtеrаl (2012-116). e, реdiсеl tо bаsе оf fl5, innеr viеw (2013-108). f, fоrе wing (2012-117)." ;
